A simple server to trace many mc server states at same time

require : 
    a usable font file for php gd2 module
    php version 5.3+ (not tested with 5.2 beyond)
    php stream_socket_client with following stream type registered
        udp(for query feature, optional)
        tcp
    php gd2 module enabled

you could also register you own config set/ templete
on the end of mc_templete_full.php